<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[المجرّد]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فعَل يفعَل، بالفتح<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[ع]</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[لَذَع]</span>: لذعت النار الشيءَ لذعاً: إِذا أحرقته.<span class="c5"> ولذعه بلسانه:</span> أي آذاه.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>... فعِل، بالكسر، يفعَل، بالفتح<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[م]</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[لَذِم]</span>: قال أبو زيد: لذِمه لذماً، مثل لزمه.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">ويقال:</span> لذِمَ بالشيء: أي أولع به.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">واللَّذِم:</span> المولع بالشيء.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>... الزيادة<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c4">[الافتعال]</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c4">[ع]</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c4">[الالتذاع]</span>: التذعتِ القرحةُ: إِذا احترقت من الوجع.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>... التفعّل<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c4">[ع]</span><a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c4">[التلذع]</span>: التلفت يميناً وشمالًا.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c5">ويقال:</span> إِن التلذّع: حسن السير وخفته. قاله الشيباني.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>